==Champions==

===Men's singles===
{{main article|2014 Italian Open – Men's Singles}}
*{{flagicon|SRB}} '''[[Novak Djokovic]]''' def. {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Rafael Nadal]], 4–6, 6–3, 6–3

===Women's singles===
{{main article|2014 Italian Open – Women's Singles}}
*{{flagicon|USA}} '''[[Serena Williams]]''' def. {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Sara Errani]], 6–3, 6–0

===Men's doubles===
{{main article|2014 Italian Open – Men's Doubles}}
*{{flagicon|CAN}} '''[[Daniel Nestor]]''' / {{flagicon|SRB}} '''[[Nenad Zimonjić]]''' def. {{flagicon|NED}} [[Robin Haase]] / {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Feliciano López]], 6–4, 7–6<sup>(7–2)</sup>

===Women's doubles===
{{main article|2014 Italian Open – Women's Doubles}}
*{{flagicon|CZE}} '''[[Květa Peschke]]''' / {{flagicon|SLO}} '''[[Katarina Srebotnik]]''' def. {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Sara Errani]] / {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Roberta Vinci]], 4–0, ret.

